ledger (2.6.2-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Ack NMU from Margarita Manterola, fixing #576660.
  * Apply patch to ledger.el from David Maus to fix some sort of reconciling
    buffer problem.  Closes: #605429.
  * Update docs to clarify that options in ~/.ledgerrc must be placed on
    separate lines.  Closes: #605810.
  * Update docs to remove unwarranted optimism about the --file option
    (It doesn't take a colon-separated list of files, and you can't specify
    it more than once).  Closes: #605807.
  * Bump standards version; no changes required.

 -- Matt Palmer <mpalmer@debian.org>  Fri, 10 Dec 2010 12:41:20 +1100

